---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Pricing — Alice Office">
  <section class="container hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">— Engagement Models</div>
    <h1>Pricing,<br/><em>plainly stated.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">Three ways we tend to work. Final scope is always sized to the brief — these are starting points, not menus.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="name">Sprint</div>
        <div class="price"><em>from</em> NT$ 120,000</div>
        <ul>
          <li>One focused deliverable</li>
          <li>2–4 week timeline</li>
          <li>Two rounds of revision</li>
          <li>Production-ready files</li>
          <li>Best for: a single piece, a small system, a packaging refresh</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="name">Project</div>
        <div class="price"><em>from</em> NT$ 380,000</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Brand or product system</li>
          <li>6–12 week timeline</li>
          <li>Strategy + design + handoff</li>
          <li>Guidelines & component library</li>
          <li>Best for: identity systems, product UI, editorial series</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="name">Retainer</div>
        <div class="price"><em>from</em> NT$ 80,000 / mo</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Ongoing systems work</li>
          <li>Quarterly commitment</li>
          <li>Weekly studio time</li>
          <li>First call on capacity</li>
          <li>Best for: in-house teams that need a senior partner</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <div class="two-col reveal">
      <h2>What's<br/>not included.</h2>
      <div>
        <p>Photography, copywriting, and printing are typically commissioned separately — we'll happily art-direct and recommend partners we trust, but we don't mark them up.</p>
        <p>Frontend implementation for product work is scoped per-engagement; for most projects we deliver design files and a component spec, and partner with your engineering team or one of our preferred build studios.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
